# Home-manager source

This tree is **HM source**. Chezmoi deploys it to **HM target** `~/.config/home-manager/`.

- Custom options: `sz.*` namespace
- New package: `modules/packages/<name>.nix` → import → flag in `szEnv.nix-hm.yaml` (sorted per yaml notes) → matching-order line in `hosts/sz.nix.tmpl`
- Host file gated by `with-nix-hm` flag; per-module enables gated by `sz.home-manager.flags`
- Do not commit `flake.lock` or `result`
- Procedures: `docs/agents/home-manager.md`
- After edits: `chezmoi apply` → `home-manager switch --flake .#sz`
